04/05/2004 Benoit PAPILLAULT <benoit.papillault@free.fr>

Comments on the kernelmode driver for GlobeSpan based USB modem
===============================================================

- usb_packets.h , usb_packets_dmt.h should be real .h files
  (add #ifndef, add proper C structure)

- choice between DMT and non DMT code should be done at usage time
  (with a module parameter) and not at compile time (using a Makefile
  settings)
